            <p>Flying via New York's John F. Kennedy International Airport (JF) can feel a bit overwhelming, but if your flight uses Terminal 4 (T4), then you are in a modern, high-tech, well-equipped space designed to make your journey smoother. T4 is one of the busiest and most essential terminals and handles a vast number of international flights. Let's learn more about the Terminal 4 JFK map. </p>
